domain.update.contracts

Interface IBasicUpdateProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBasicObserver, IBasicUpdateSource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IUpdateProcessor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionInput, BasicUpdateProcessor, CompositeAction, CompositeActionFly, CompositeActionFlyCatch, ForcedRemiseObserver, GameController, InputProvider, OutOfMovesObserver, PromotionObserver, UpdateProcessor, UpdatePropagator

    public interface IBasicUpdateProcessor
extends IBasicObserver, IBasicUpdateSource
    Combines IBasicUpdateSource with IBasicObserver to form an IBasicUpdateProcessor. This interface is typically employed to directly propagate any updates it receives from its observees to its observers. However, any instance that observes updates, processes them and emits them again can use this interface.
